# BluffAI — Liar’s Dice Solver

## WIP

This project explores how modern poker AI techniques can be used to **solve and play Liar’s Dice**, the bluffing dice game popularised by the Steam game *Liar’s Bar*.

Liar’s Dice is a game of **imperfect information** that requires **mixed strategies, belief modelling, and bluffing** — the same core challenges found in poker AI.

This project is inspired by **Libratus** and modern imperfect-information game research:  
https://thegradient.pub/libratus-poker/
